net.nemerosa.ontrack.model.support

Interface StartupService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtensionManagerImpl, IndexationServiceImpl, JobStartup, MainDBStartupService, ValidationRunStatusServiceImpl

    public interface StartupService
    Implement this interface and declare the implementation as a @Component if you want to execute some code at start-up, after the database has been initialized or migrated.
